{"tid":46000,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"聖誕到喇，可以幫我一個忙嗎...","createTime":"2016-12-19T10:41:14.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-20T04:14:02.000Z","uid":36713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2b78e27469b4dff726ef06a34c72217d384eb8e0","tid":46000,"uid":36713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T10:41:14.000Z","msg":"第一次開post 希望各位巴絲可以幫下手。<br />\n有一位好天真既小朋友，仍然相信世界上有聖誕老人既存在，佢好希望聖誕老人可以送份禮物比佢。<br />\n我已經搵過好多鋪頭都冇，但聖誕節將至，我好希望可以完到佢實現依個願望。<br />\n<br />\n我想搵一架 Tomica puv03既車仔<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/19/183823_05d0f3efae70dc7e83eb1a3517156db7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F19%2F183823_05d0f3efae70dc7e83eb1a3517156db7.jpg&h=8001bb7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如果搵到可唔可以通知聲我狗衝去買。唔該各位巴絲"},{"pid":"4da3fc3f39a5823d93c3458f76ba4c8fd76bb5c3","tid":46000,"uid":9726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T04:14:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}